
☠ MORTAL FRETS — The Fretboard Slayer
Retro arcade-style guitar fretboard trainer inspired by Mortal Kombat. 8 game modes across Identification and Construction. Global leaderboard powered by Firebase.
🎮 Play Now

Game Modes
All modes: 10 questions per round · Score = errors (fewer = better) · Tiebreaker: time
Identification — see the question on the fretboard, press the correct button
ModeWhat you seeWhat you doNote IDDot on fretboard (frets 0–12, all strings)Press the correct note nameInterval IDR (root, red) + interval dot within ±3 frets/±2 stringsPress the correct interval (m2–P8)Chord IDReal voicing — triads on 3 adjacent strings, tetrads as Drop 2 / Drop 3 / Drop 2+4Press the correct chord typeScale IDFull scale in a 5-fret box, R = RootPress the correct scale name
Construction — target illuminated, build it on the fretboard, press SUBMIT
ModeWhat you seeWhat you doNote ConstructionTarget note illuminatedPlace ALL occurrences on the fretboardInterval ConstructionR pre-placed (red), interval illuminatedClick anywhere to place the note — auto-checks immediatelyChord ConstructionOne chord tone pre-placed (amber, with role R/3/5/7)Place remaining notes, one per stringScale ConstructionR pre-placed in boxFill all scale positions

Rules

Variety: same type appears at most twice per round; exact same question never repeats
Wrong answer (ID): retry same question, timer keeps running
Wrong SUBMIT (Construction): wrong dots → red, missing → orange; click to fix, re-SUBMIT
Mercy ☠: activates after 2 wrong answers — hold to reveal solution, release to retry
Box selection: Chord and Scale modes — fixed 5-fret box or 💀 KHAOS (random each question)
Notation: toggle A-B-C / Do-Re-Mi at any time


Active Chords & Scales
Before starting, deselect chord or scale types you want to skip. Deselected types show ✕ in the lobby and in-game. The leaderboard supports two views: ALL (everyone) or SAME CONFIG (only entries with your same selection).

Scoring
ErrorsResult0⚡ FLAWLESS VICTORY1–2EXCELLENT FIGHTER3–5SKILLED WARRIOR6–10FIGHT HARDER11–19FINISH HIM20+FATALITY

Music Theory Coverage
Notes: all 12 chromatic, frets 0–12, all 6 strings (standard tuning E A D G B e)
Intervals: m2 · M2 · m3 · M3 · P4 · TT · P5 · m6 · M6 · m7 · M7 · P8
Chords: Maj · min · Aug · Dim · Maj7 · Dom7 · min7 · ø7 · °7
Scales: Major · Natural Minor · Harmonic Minor · Melodic Minor · Whole-Half Dim · Half-Whole Dim
Voicings: triads on all 4 adjacent 3-string groups · Drop 2, Drop 3, Drop 2+4 on all adjacent 4-string groups · all inversions

Deploy

Upload mortal_frets.html renamed as index.html
GitHub Settings → Pages → branch main → / (root)


Firebase Setup
Uses Firebase Realtime Database REST API (no SDK).

console.firebase.google.com → new project → Realtime Database
Replace FB_CONFIG near the top of the <script> tag
Set rules:

json{
  "rules": {
    "leaderboards": {
      "$mode": { ".read": true, ".write": true }
    }
  }
}

Tech
Pure HTML/CSS/JS · Web Audio API · SVG fretboard · Firebase REST API · Press Start 2P + Rajdhani · CRT scanlines
